                      "ep_id": 3705,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/14/237301566/2899a9fa6efec1006150467a00823c4a_8990591855736742104.png",
                      "name": "Чудовищный креститель",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4268,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/09/124137736/f98dc430d216467224c9809af7102ceb_7338452602545485866.png",
                      "name": "Необычная запчасть",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "In the Wake of Narcissus",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When Seymour completed his mission and found his Master Mary-Ann, she told him to live the way Seymour himself wanted, and he chose to return to Mamere. He invited her to go on a journey with him, Oceanid Ann and Mary-Ann, and she happily agreed. During the time that Seymour was away, Mamere began to explore other styles of painting, and even other Melusines, who had previously not understood Mamere's paintings, began to admire them. Before her journey, Mamere left Traveler a painting in a new style, where she painted herself, Seymour, Traveler, and Paimon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/10/237301566/43dc4ae6e6d11487085b4d3722d830b1_1717087209660849863.png"
